So far--no work with the RNG, no ghost voices, and nothing that even 
resembles speech. I have a Bill chip, and even that isn&#39;t doing 
anything, but could be my set-up. I think what I want to try is load 
an EEPROM by hand wiht the numbers for  various allophones, then use 
the RNG to access the memory, and send it to the Speakjet. So far 
though, nothing beats a box, in whatever form it&#39;s in. 

 Frank-S

